text:
A good way to think of single doses of a #COVIDVaccine *after a few weeks* is as an extra (imperfect) layer of protection.
So:

- Outdoor activities+space - probably safe✅

- Well ventilated spaces with masks - probably safe ✅

- Indoor coughing competitions - still not safe ❌
